HEADWORD: gatecrasher
<hw>gate"crash`er</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>A person who enters into a
party or other social event without an invitation, or into a theater or
other public performance without a ticket.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

